{
  "id": "adv_love_2311_08_03",
  "title": "Episode 8 Part 3",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "outsidehall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "やり直したいと伝える",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_heart-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 69.666656494
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-koh009.m4a",
              "text": "もう一度……やり直さないか？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Shall we… get back together?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 69.666656494,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-ngs004.m4a",
              "text": "……どうして、今更そんなこと言うの？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…Why are you saying that now‚\nafter all this time?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 73.1666564941,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-koh011.m4a",
              "text": "俺は……ずっと後悔してた。離れて初めて\n幼い頃からずっとそばにいてくれた\n渚の大切さに気付いたんだ。だから……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I… I've regretted it ever since.\nI realized only after we were apart\nhow precious you are‚ since you are\nwho have always been with me‚ so…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 77.0999898274,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-ngs005.m4a",
              "text": "……ありがとう、嬉しい",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…Thank you. I'm glad.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 88.2333257039,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": null,
              "text": "じゃあ……！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Then…!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 91.2999928792,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 91.6104036053
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-ngs006.m4a",
              "text": "でも、ダメだよ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "But‚ it's not possible.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 92.233329773,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-koh012.m4a",
              "text": "え……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Huh…?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 94.4999964397,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 95.533329773
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-ngs007.m4a",
              "text": "私だって{user}くんと別れて\nすっごく辛かった。それでもなんとか\n立ち直ろうって今まで頑張ってきたんだよ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "It was so painful for me to break up\nwith you‚{user}-kun.\nBut I've been trying my best to\nmove on.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 95.533329773,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-ngs008.m4a",
              "text": "それなのに……今更\nそんなこと言われても……無理だよ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "We've come too far…\nwhat you said is impossible…\nit's too late",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 104.0333287557,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
                  "delay": 7600.002034500008
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-koh013.m4a",
              "text": "あ……渚！\n待ってくれ……渚……！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Ah… Nagisa!\nWait… Nagisa…!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 114.0999867756,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-ngs009.m4a",
              "text": "ごめんね、{user}くん\n大好きだったよ……さよなら",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I'm sorry‚ {user}-kun.\nI loved you… goodbye.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 118.7666580199,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "何も言えない",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_heart-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 125.9333185831
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-koh014.m4a",
              "text": "俺ともう一度……いや、なんでもない\nただ、久しぶりに渚の顔が見たかったんだ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Can we get back… no‚ it's nothing.\nI just wanted to see your face again\nafter all this time‚ Nagisa.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 125.9333185831,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-ngs010.m4a",
              "text": "……そっか\n私も、{user}くんの\n顔が見れて良かった",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…I see.\nIt was good to see you again‚ too‚\n{user}-kun.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 134.9999852497,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-ngs011.m4a",
              "text": "でも……会うのはこれっきりにしよっか",
              "translations": {
                "en": "But…\nlet's never see each other again.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 140.2999740599,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-koh015.m4a",
              "text": "え……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Huh…?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 144.2333216348,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-ngs012.m4a",
              "text": "その方がお互いのためだと思うんだ\nそれじゃあ……バイバイ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I think that's better for\nboth of us. Well then… goodbye.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 145.3999872842,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
                  "delay": 7733.337783899998
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-koh016.m4a",
              "text": "渚……！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Nagisa…!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 155.0666549679,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 156.3999809261
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 157.6999809261
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-koh017.m4a",
              "text": "ただいま",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I'm home.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 158.5999842322,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
                  "delay": 1554.361343700009
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "smr",
              "speakerName": "すみれ",
              "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-smr001.m4a",
              "text": "おかえりお兄ちゃん……って\nど、どうしたの！？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Welcome back‚ big brother… wait‚\nw-what's wrong!?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 161.699963887,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-koh018.m4a",
              "text": "いや……なんでもないよ\n何もなかった……いや\n何も……言えなかった",
              "translations": {
                "en": "It's nothing… Nothing happened…\nNo‚ I could say… nothing…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 166.599963887,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "smr",
              "speakerName": "すみれ",
              "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-smr002.m4a",
              "text": "お兄ちゃん……良かったら\n話してくれない？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Big brother… if you're okay‚\nwill you tell me what happened?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 176.7999577835,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-koh019.m4a",
              "text": "すみれ……実は……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Sumire-chan… actually…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 182.9332911169,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 186.3999656674
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 187.6999656674
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "smr",
              "speakerName": "すみれ",
              "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-smr003.m4a",
              "text": "そっか……渚ちゃんと……\nでも、確かにその方が\nお兄ちゃんにとってもいいと思うよ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I see… you and Nagisa-chan…\nbut I think that's better for you too",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 188.566623433,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "smr",
              "speakerName": "すみれ",
              "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-smr004.m4a",
              "text": "お兄ちゃんも、渚ちゃんも……\n本当にお互いのことが好きだった\nでも、お別れした",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Both you and Nagisa-chan…\nreally loved each other.\nBut you broke up.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 199.2999699906,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "smr",
              "speakerName": "すみれ",
              "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-smr005.m4a",
              "text": "それはきっと、一言じゃ言えないくらい\nいろんなことが重なったんだと思う",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I'm sure it was because of\na lot of complicated reasons.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 207.5999699906,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "smr",
              "speakerName": "すみれ",
              "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-smr006.m4a",
              "text": "もし二人がこれからも会うことになったら\n渚ちゃんはお兄ちゃんと会うたびに\n楽しい時間だけじゃなくて……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "If you two continue to see each other‚\nwhenever Nagisa-chan see you‚\nshe will remember\nnot only the happy moments…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 214.4666366573,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "smr",
              "speakerName": "すみれ",
              "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-smr007.m4a",
              "text": "うまくいかなかった苦しい時間を\n思い出しちゃうんじゃないかな\nだから……もう会わないようにした",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…but also the painful moments\nwhen things weren't going well.\nThat's why… she decided to\nnever see you again.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 225.3999699906,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-koh020.m4a",
              "text": "そう……なのかな。いや、そうかもしれない\n別れ際の渚は……泣いてた",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Is that… what it is?\nNo‚ you're probably right.\nNagisa was… crying\nwhen she said goodbye.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 236.0666366573,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "smr",
              "speakerName": "すみれ",
              "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_03-smr008.m4a",
